{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji27.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给黄炎培的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给黄炎培的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年10月5日）任之先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三日惠示敬悉。盛意可感！在共同纲领发布之后，我似不宜迅即重复说一遍共同纲领里说过的话，如像经济问题等事。因此，除公告外，暂时不拟发表个人文件，这样似较适宜。此复。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬颂大安！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月五日[1]黄炎培，中国民主建国会主要负责人。当时任中央人民政府委员。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":5}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":376,"page_end":376},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}